<!doctype html>
<html lang="pl">
<%- include('../../partials/head') %>
<body class="bg-surface text-on-surface font-body antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<%- include('../../partials/header', { showBack: false, showAuth: true }) %>

<main class="flex-1 pt-24 pb-32 px-6 max-w-md mx-auto w-full">
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-4 tracking-tight">Możemy Ci pomóc.</h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant opacity-90">
      dlaczegozyc.pl to spokojna przestrzeń pełna inspiracji, anonimowa skrzynka do dzielenia się myślami oraz łatwy dostęp do profesjonalnego wsparcia.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
    <a href="/help" class="relative group overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container p-6 rounded-[2rem] text-left transition-transform active:scale-95 duration-200 shadow-sm block">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
        <div class="bg-white/20 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-12">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary text-3xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">line_end</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-primary mb-1">Pomoc</h2>
          <p class="text-on-primary/80 text-sm">Uzyskaj natychmiastowe wsparcie profesjonalistów i dostęp do linii zaufania.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <a href="/inspirations" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-5 rounded-[2rem] text-left flex flex-col justify-between transition-colors hover:bg-surface-container-low active:scale-95 duration-200 block">
        <div class="text-primary mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">auto_awesome</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface">Inspiracja</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-1">Historie, które dają nadzieję.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/anonymous-box" class="bg-tertiary-container p-5 rounded-[2rem] text-left flex flex-col justify-between transition-colors hover:bg-tertiary-fixed-dim active:scale-95 duration-200 block">
        <div class="text-tertiary mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">inventory_2</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface">Skrzynka</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs mt-1">Anonimowy głos Twoich myśli.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mt-12 p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl text-center">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline-variant mb-2">shield_with_heart</span>
    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-medium">Bezpieczeństwo i anonimowość są naszym priorytetem.</p>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../../partials/navigation-public') %>
</body>
</html>
